Up for sale is a 2014 RWS Diana 34 Pro Compact, with an upgraded Premium Diana Stock (these were limited edition).  The gun has a Vortek Kit installed and shoots at about 850fps.  It is in excellent, near new condition, and has never been dry-fired.  It has seen about 1 tin of pellets through it.  The trigger is crisp and light, and the gun shoots hard and accurate.  The most accurate pellets are H&N FTT 4.50mm Pellets and H&N Sniper Medium 8.5gr Pellets.  It has a MUCH nicer shot cycle thanks to the Vortek kit.

The last items included are the original Diana mainspring, a new spare Vortek spring, and numerous extra parts, screws, nuts, and seals that I bought as spares (at least $50 in parts and seals).

RWS 34 Pro Compact - $300

Scope - $200

Extra Springs, Parts & Seals - $50
